summary: Rework on Aela - The Huntress face.
descriptionHtml:
============================================================================================
[b]Description[/b]

Hi, im BlackEffect, and im releasing an face rework of the Aela - The Huntress, i hope you like it a give any suggestions you want to.

============================================================================================
[b]Installation[/b]

Just copy the files to \\Skyrim\\Data folder and make sure the .esp is activated on Data Files.

============================================================================================
[b]Credits[/b]

Apachii Sky Hair
HD Eyes
HD TintMasks
Mature Body and Face Textures
Extended Slide Colors


============================================================================================
[b]Permissions[/b]
Do NOT edit my mod and release as yours, if you find a bug, ask me what is happening, what bug you found and if you want to fix anything, you MUST ask me first. Nexus Exclusive Mod.
